    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先确认一下参与者：User、SchedulerApp、Event实体、EventDAO、Reminder实体、ReminderService。这样六个参与者够吗？Event和Reminder需要持久化存储，所以要有对应的DAO层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
