    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，六个参与者。Event和Reminder都是临时创建的对象，通过DAO落盘。流程上，用户发起添加事件请求后，SchedulerApp创建Event对象，这里要关联ClassroomService这个教育场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前半段画出来：User向SchedulerApp发送添加事件请求，SchedulerApp创建Event并传入Education_ClassroomService参数，然后Event调用EventDAO的add_event方法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "add event",
        "new"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
