    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，add_event这里有个细节——持久化的时候要关联GradeSync服务，因为事件数据需要同步到成绩系统。所以是EventDAO去处理这个GradeSync的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventDAO",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "add_event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整为Event通过异步消息调用EventDAO的add_event，并传入Education_GradeSync。然后EventDAO返回确认给SchedulerApp。前半段完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
