      "utterance": "好的，我把查看流程补上：User请求view events，SchedulerApp调用EventDAO的get_events_for_day并传入Education_ClassroomService，然后返回列表，最后SchedulerApp展示给用户。整个图应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
